---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Founder — Nous Ergon"
  description="Brian McMahon founded Nous Ergon, an applied AI lab, in March 2026. His background intersects tech and finance — a decade in finance, then almost a decade in data and AI engineering."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-12">
    <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Brian McMahon</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mb-8">Founder</p>

    <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Brian founded Nous Ergon in March 2026 to build agentic systems
      addressing problems with measurable, continuously verifiable outcomes.
      His background intersects tech and finance.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
      He spent a decade in finance, primarily investment banking and
      investment advisory, followed by almost a decade in data and AI
      engineering, most recently at Block. He holds an MBA in Finance from
      CEIBS and London Business School, and an MS in Computer Science
      (machine learning) from Georgia Tech. The full background is on
      <a class="text-sky-400 hover:text-sky-300 transition" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/brian-c-mcmahon/">LinkedIn</a>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-sky-400 mb-3">Links</h2>
    <ul class="text-sm md:text-base text-zinc-300 space-y-1">
      <li><a class="text-sky-400 hover:text-sky-300 transition" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/brian-c-mcmahon/">LinkedIn</a></li>
      <li><a class="text-sky-400 hover:text-sky-300 transition" href="https://github.com/cipher813">GitHub</a></li>
      <li><a class="text-sky-400 hover:text-sky-300 transition" href="mailto:brian@nousergon.ai">brian@nousergon.ai</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</Base>
